title: Audiophile Seasonal Music-Cantante Domino, Ceremony of Angels
description:
Audiophile classy (!) seasonal music. 

Cantante Domino is on the Swedish Proprius label, who brought you Jazz at the Pawnshop. It was recorded live  using just two microphones into a Revox A77 reel to reel recorder. The music and ambience are excellent. 

Ceremony of Angels is on the Golden String Audiophile label from Japan and features works by Back, Beethove, Mozart, Britten etc, and features solo harp and the Toyko Girls Choir. Sonics again are excellent
